reviewText:
Zara Whites is my favorite porn star since Marilyn Chambers. Abandon and amusement

are her 2 most frequent screen emotions. In this movie, amusement predominates. This is

a parody of porn, and Zara is quite amusing in addition to being sexy and beautiful(and,

at least within the confines of this particular movie, a good actress). My only complaint is

that the movie deserves its "R" rating. It could have been produced by Playboy Films,

lots of T & A and sex without views of the vital sex organs or penetration seen.

I consider this a waste of Zara's best talents, although it's never disappointing to see

naked anyone as beautiful and sexy as Zara Whites.
